title.narrative: 5.3 PROGRAMME PLANNING, MONITORING & EVALUATION

description.narrative: Programme planning and monitoring: UNICEF staff and partners are provided with guidance, tools and resources to effectively plan and monitor programmes., which contributes to Cross-Sectoral Monitoring, Data And Situation Analyses, Cross-Sectoral Planning And Programme Reviews, Evaluation And Research. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Evaluations, Research And Data, Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Capacities of subnational institutions are enhanced for child-sensitive and participatory social policy planning to support vulnerable girls and boys.
